on\">\n                        Intensywna czerwona barwa z cegłastymi przeblyskami. Bukiet niezwykle złożony z dominującymi akcentami dojrzałych ciemnych wiśni i śliwek oraz bogactwem aromatów orzechów, czarnej herbaty, lukrecji i przypraw korzennych.\n                    </p>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"wine-alcohol\">Vol: 9%</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>   \n    </div>\n    \n       <div class=\"row\">\n       <div class=\"wine-card\">\n        <div class=\"wine-card-inner\">\n            <!-- Left side - Wine image (20%) -->\n            <div class=\"wine-image\">\n                <img src=\"wine-bottle.png\" alt=\"Bertani Amarone della Valpolicella\">\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Right side - Wine info (80%) -->\n            <div class=\"wine-content\">\n                <!-- Row 1 - Title and Prices in one row -->\n                <div class=\"wine-header-row\">\n                    <h1 class=\"wine-title\">BERTANI AMARONE DELLA VALPOLICELLA CLASSICO DOCG</h1>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"wine-prices\">\n                        <div class=\"price-badge\">\n                          <span class=\"price-volume\">100ml <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><title>wine-glass-france-french-nation-holiday</title><g fill=\"#454444\"><path d=\"M18.43 9.1c-0.19-1.55-1.47-5.92-1.53-6.11a0.19 0.19 0 0 0-0.18-0.14h-9.12a0.19 0.19 0 0 0-0.18 0.14c-0.05 0.19-1.33 4.56-1.53 6.11-0.18 1.46 0.29 2.91 1.33 4.08 1.18 1.34 2.94 2.15 4.75 2.2v5.71h-3.61a0.19 0.19 0 0 0 0 0.38h7.6a0.19 0.19 0 0 0 0-0.38h-3.61v-5.71c1.8-0.05 3.57-0.86 4.75-2.2 1.04-1.17 1.51-2.62 1.33-4.08z m-10.69-5.87h8.84a116.49 116.49 0 0 1 0.93 3.42h-10.7c0.37-1.45 0.8-2.96 0.93-3.42z m9.07 9.7c-1.15 1.3-2.89 2.08-4.65 2.08s-3.5-0.78-4.65-2.08c-0.97-1.09-1.4-2.44-1.24-3.79 0.06-0.48 0.23-1.27 0.44-2.11h10.9c0.21 0.84 0.38 1.63 0.44 2.11 0.17 1.35-0.27 2.69-1.24