  {
    "id": "fa82670b-7d43-4694-ad72-49bada3cae12",
    "name": "A4-2kolumny-6wierszy",
    "description": "",
    "category": "general",
    "htmlContent": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"pl\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Karta Win – 2 kolumny × 6 wierszy</title>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<style>\n  * {margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}\n  @page {size:A4;margin:0;}\n\n  body {\n    \n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    background: #000000;\n    padding: 10mm;\n       {{#if collection.pdfBackground}}\n    background: url('{{collection.pdfBackground}}') center/cover no-repeat;\n    {{/if}}\n  }\n\n  .a4-page {\n    width: 210mm;\n    min-height: 297mm;\n    \n    border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    margin: 0 auto 10mm auto;\n    padding: 10mm;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; /* 2 kolumny */\n    grid-auto-rows: calc((297mm - 20mm - (5 * 3mm)) / 6); /* 6 wierszy */\n    gap: 3mm 6mm; /* pion / poziom */\n  }\n\n  .category {\n    grid-column: 1 / -1; /* kategoria na całą szerokość */\n    margin-bottom: 3mm;\n  }\n\n  .category h1 {\n    background: #000;\n    color: #fff;\n    font-size: 14pt;\n    padding: 6px;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 3mm;\n  }\n\n  .wines-list {\n    display: contents; /* elementy idą bezpośrednio w grid */\n  }\n\n  .wine-card {\n    border: 1px solid #ddd;\n    padding: 3mm 4mm;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n\n  .wine-card-inner {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 15% 85%;\n    gap: 3mm;\n    height: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .wine-image {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .wine-image img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: contain;\n  }\n\n  .wine-content {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .wine-header-row {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 2mm;\n    margin-bottom: 1mm;\n  }\n\n  .wine-title {\n    font-size: 10pt;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    color: #111;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n  }\n\n  .wine-prices {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: flex-end;\n    gap: 1mm;\n    font-size: 7pt;\n  }\n\n  .price-badge {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: flex-end;\n    gap: 2mm;\n    line-height: 1;\n  }\n\n  .price-volume {\n    color: #666;\n    font-size: 7pt;\n  }\n\n  .price-amount {\n    font-size: 8pt;\n    border: 1px solid #000;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 1px 6px;\n  }\n\n  .wine-details {\n    font-size: 7pt;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .wine-description {\n    font-size: 7pt;\n    color: #333;\n    text-align: justify;\n    margin-top: 1mm;\n    display: -webkit-box;\n    -webkit-line-clamp: 2; /* maks 2 linie */\n    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .wine-alcohol {\n    font-size: 6.5pt;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-top: 1mm;\n    color: #555;\n  }\n\n  @media print {\n    body {\n      background: white;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    .a4-page {\n      border: none;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 10mm;\n      page-break-after: always;\n    }\n\n    .category {\n      break-inside: avoid;\n      page-break-inside: avoid;\n    }\n\n    .wine-card {\n      break-inside: avoid;\n      page-break-inside: avoid;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"a4-page\" id=\"content\"></div>\n\n<script>\n// Dane przykładowe\nconst wines = [\n  { name: \"Chianti Classico\", category: \"Wina czerwone\", szczepy: \"Sangiovese\", region: \"Toskania\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Intensywna czerwona barwa z ceglastymi przebłyskami. Bukiet niezwykle złożony z dominującymi akcentami dojrzałych ciemnych wiśni i śliwek oraz bogactwem aromatów orzechów, czarnej herbaty.\", alcohol: \"13.5%\", image: \"/uploads/wine1.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Merlot Riserva\", category: \"Wina czerwone\", szczepy: \"Merlot\", region: \"Włochy\", type: \"Półwytrawne\", description: \"Gładkie, zrównoważone, aromaty czerwonych owoców i czekolady.\", alcohol: \"13%\", image: \"/uploads/wine3.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Chardonnay\", category: \"Wina białe\", szczepy: \"Chardonnay\", region: \"Burgundia\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Aromatyczne wino o nutach jabłka, masła i wanilii.\", alcohol: \"12.5%\", image: \"/uploads/wine4.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Riesling\", category: \"Wina białe\", szczepy: \"Riesling\", region: \"Niemcy\", type: \"Półwytrawne\", description: \"Świeże i cytrusowe z lekką słodyczą.\", alcohol: \"11%\", image: \"/uploads/wine5.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Prosecco\", category: \"Wina musujące\", szczepy: \"Glera\", region: \"Wenecja Euganejska\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Delikatne bąbelki, lekko owocowe, przyjemne w ustach.\", alcohol: \"11%\", image: \"/uploads/wine6.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Lambrusco\", category: \"Wina musujące\", szczepy: \"Lambrusco\", region: \"Emilia-Romania\", type: \"Półsłodkie\", description: \"Lekkie, musujące, przyjemnie owocowe.\", alcohol: \"10.5%\", image: \"/uploads/wine7.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Malbec Reserva\", category: \"Wina czerwone\", szczepy: \"Malbec\", region: \"Mendoza\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Pełne, ciemne, z nutami jeżyn, czekolady i wanilii.\", alcohol: \"14%\", image: \"/uploads/wine8.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Pinot Grigio\", category: \"Wina białe\", szczepy: \"Pinot Grigio\", region: \"Włochy\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Lekkie, świeże, aromaty jabłka i cytrusów.\", alcohol: \"12%\", image: \"/uploads/wine9.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Cabernet Sauvignon\", category: \"Wina czerwone\", szczepy: \"Cabernet Sauvignon\", region: \"Chile\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Głębokie, bogate w taniny z aromatami czarnej porzeczki i pieprzu.\", alcohol: \"13.5%\", image: \"/uploads/wine10.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Sauvignon Blanc\", category: \"Wina białe\", szczepy: \"Sauvignon Blanc\", region: \"Nowa Zelandia\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Świeże, ziołowe z nutami agrestu i cytryny.\", alcohol: \"12%\", image: \"/uploads/wine11.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Moscato d’Asti\", category: \"Wina musujące\", szczepy: \"Moscato\", region: \"Piemont\", type: \"Słodkie\", description: \"Lekko musujące, bardzo aromatyczne z nutą brzoskwini.\", alcohol: \"5.5%\", image: \"/uploads/wine12.jpg\" },\n  { name: \"Cava Brut\", category: \"Wina musujące\", szczepy: \"Macabeo, Parellada, Xarel-lo\", region: \"Hiszpania\", type: \"Wytrawne\", description: \"Drobne bąbelki, świeży aromat cytrusów i tostów.\", alcohol: \"11.5%\", image: \"/uploads/wine13.jpg\" },\n];\n\n// Grupowanie wg kategorii\nconst grouped = wines.reduce((acc, wine) => {\n  if (!acc[wine.category]) acc[wine.category] = [];\n  acc[wine.category].push(wine);\n  return acc;\n}, {});\n\n// Renderowanie kategorii\nconst container = document.getElementById('content');\nfor (const [category, wineList] of Object.entries(grouped)) {\n  const section = document.createElement('div');\n  section.classList.add('category');\n  section.innerHTML = `\n    <h1>${category}</h1>\n    <div class=\"wines-list\">\n      ${wineList.map(wine => `\n        <div class=\"wine-card\">\n          <div class=\"wine-card-inner\">\n            <div class=\"wine-image\">\n              <img src=\"https://witrynarium.pl/images/przyklad.jpg\" alt=\"${wine.name}\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"wine-content\">\n              <div class=\"wine-header-row\">\n                <div class=\"wine-title\">${wine.name}</div>\n                <div class=\"wine-prices\">\n                  <div class=\"price-badge\"><span class=\"price-volume\">100ml</span><span class=\"price-amount\">39zł</span></div>\n                  <div class=\"price-badge\"><span class=\"price-volume\">750ml</span><span class=\"price-amount\">139zł</span></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"wine-details\">\n                <div><strong>Szczep:</strong> ${wine.szczepy}</div>\n                <div><strong>Region:</strong> ${wine.region}</div>\n                <div><strong>Typ:</strong> ${wine.type}</div>\n                <p class=\"wine-description\">${wine.description}</p>\n                <div class=\"wine-alcohol\">Vol: ${wine.alcohol}</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      `).join('')}\n    </div>\n  `;\n  container.appendChild(section);\n}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
    "cssContent": "/* Dodatkowe style CSS */\n.wine-card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n@media print {\n    body {\n        background: white;\n    }\n    \n    .wine-card {\n        box-shadow: none;\n        border: 1px solid #ddd;\n    }\n}",
